data.description:
Discover this enchanting single-story residence with four bedrooms and three bathrooms. Embrace the spacious open layout, adorned with a sizable kitchen island, granite countertops, a walk-in pantry, and a gas cooktop. Enjoy the additional entertainment room and the convenience of a spacious master bath boasting dual walk-in closets.

This home also features a dedicated study, abundant storage space, a gas fireplace with an electric starter, and an extended covered outdoor living area. Simplify your parking needs with the three-car tandem garage. It's a home designed for comfort and style.


A seller concession of $8000 is offered to the buyer, allowing them to either lower the interest rate or cover closing cost
